title: Triangle Adventures Workshop
content: Hey Programmers! Introducing the very first workshop of the year: TRIANGLE ADVENTURES! Here you can find a google doc containing an overview of the workshop and necessary files. You can also watch this video detailing how the set up the workshop in Eclipse and a sample solution to level 1. Bring any questions you may have to next week's general meeting or feel free to email us.

title: Challenge Problem Survey
content: Hey everyone! When you have time, please take this survey to help us improve our challenge problems! It's pretty short (1-3 minutes), and you may even get leaderboard points for it... 😉 To clarify: We're currently posting challenge problems right before programming club meetings (every other week). This might change depending on the survey results.
